Description: Assembler for LEGO MINDSTORMS EV3
 Assembler for LEGO MINDSTORMS EV3 About lmsasm is a tool to compile
 LEGO MINDSTORMS EV3 bytecode language files (.lms) into LEGO MINDSTORMS
 EV3 VM executable files (.rbf).
 .
 This particular version is a reimplementation of the lmsasm
 tool that is part of the official EV3 Firmware Source Code
 (http://www.lego.com/en-us/mindstorms/downloads).  Disclaimer LEGOÂ®
